Defendant Brian D. Schneider in court with attorney Jorge R Fragoso.  Kevin Michael Osborne appeared for the State of Wisconsin.  Defendant enters a guilty plea to Count 1.  Court finds defendant guilty.  Count 2 dismissed and read in.

    The Defendant was given the following:

WITHHELD SENTENCE;  Credit for 3 days if revoked.

TERM OF PROBATION:  1 YEAR; Early release from probation is left up to the Agent

CONDITIONS OF PROBATION:  
*AODA Assessment and follow through with any treatment recommended;
*Absolute Sobriety;  Random U.A.'s ; 
*No Use or Possession of alcohol, controlled substances or drug paraphernalia.
*Follow through with any treatment and/or counseling recommended by Agent;
*DNA sample to be provided if not yet previously done.

COURT COSTS:  $243.00 (to be paid as a condition of probation);

DNA SURCHARGE:  $200.00 (to be paid as a condition of probation);

CONDITION TIME: 30 days, STAYED; to be used at agent's discretion.  Agent to determine with or without non working hours.
